    <content>&lt;P&gt;You can also check out this configuration by following this SAP Tech Bytes video... SAP Tech Bytes: Configuring SAP S/4HANA Cloud and SAP Integration Suite, advanced event mesh&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;div class="video-embed-center video-embed"&gt;&lt;iframe class="embedly-embed" src="https://cdn.embedly.com/widgets/media.html?src=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F6hb9l0ss5ec%3Ffeature%3Doembed&amp;amp;display_name=YouTube&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6hb9l0ss5ec&amp;amp;image=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F6hb9l0ss5ec%2Fhqdefault.jpg&amp;amp;key=b0d40caa4f094c68be7c29880b16f56e&amp;amp;type=text%2Fhtml&amp;amp;schema=youtube" width="600" height="337" scrolling="no" title="SAP Tech Bytes: Configuring SAP S/4HANA Cloud and SAP Integration Suite, advanced event mesh" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture;" allowfullscreen="true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;Steps: &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;A class="" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6hb9l0ss5ec&amp;amp;t=4s" target="" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;00:04&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt; Introduction &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;A class="" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6hb9l0ss5ec&amp;amp;t=39s" target="" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;00:39&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt; SAP Help documentation &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;A class="" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6hb9l0ss5ec&amp;amp;t=103s" target="" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;01:43&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt; Maintain Client Certificates in SAP S/4HANA Cloud &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&